    "For highperforming LLMs, the model provides reasonable reasoning steps and clear descriptive information, effectively guiding the subsequent selection process.",
    "The average number of reasoning steps is 3.4, indicating that the LLM considers multiple steps during reasoning.",
    "We also found that, during the reasoning process, the LLM integrates the global semantic description of the image to infer or correct unreasonable text queries, thereby enhancing interpretability and improving robustness.",
